➜延庆山地小米十月秋收，150天修炼期只为这一碗米油浓稠小米粥
http://www.sohu.com/a/427376204_100477	26530
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201026/c83a1fd8942c4757a65cf0f3a93f6393.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201026/313756acc92743ffa9dc04ef3bf07535.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201026/0d1fcb89ba604150809124614b3cbb6c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>“ 打谷子去！”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">清晨8点，延庆的秋凉像隔壁大爷家炊烟一样，正慢慢散开。后山遛早回来，我们遇上了扛着犁耙出门的时大哥。</p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
